summary: Small cabin in the woods with see through windows (no loading screens).
descriptionHtml:
[center][color=#f1c232][size=5]Reifnir's Cabin[/size][/color][/center]
Reifnir's Cabin is a small player house located in pine forest in Falkreath Hold. There are no loading screens so you can see through windows.
It was designed for hunter character, but it should be suitable for everyone who likes small houses.


[size=4]Storage:

[/size][list]
[*]Potions
[*]Poisons
[*]2 Firewood piles (linked)
[*]Notes
[*]Books & journals

[*]Armor
[*]Weapons

[*]Hides and pelts
[*]Smithing supplies
[*]Tools
[*]Food
[*]Beverages
[*]Dishes
[*]Strongbox
[*]Chest
[*]2 barrels on porch
[/list][list]
[*]Bookshelf for 18 books
[/list]
[size=4]Other features:
[/size]
[list]
[*]Anvil
[*]Tanning Rack
[*]Grindstone
[*]Wood Chopping Block
[*]Workbench
[*]Cooking Pot
[*]Alchemy Lab
[/list]

All clutter is static. There's no rain inside house. Bed gives Well Rested Bonus. Fully Navmeshed. Cleaned with TES5Edit.


[size=4]Credits:

[/size]DarkFox127 - Weather Clipping script
author: balcer
